high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then turn right at the microwave.
Take the apple from the microwave.
Move left to the end of the counter.
Put the apple in the silver bin to the left of the counter.
Turn right, go straight to the sink.
Take the apple on the left drying rack.
Turn around, go straight then turn right at the end of the counter on the right.
Put the apple in the silver bin to the left of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and remove the green apple out of the microwave, then close the microwave door.
Turn around and take a step forward, the turn right and take another step forward, turn right again to face the counter.
Place the green apple into the back left corner of the small grey trash can that is to the left of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the green apple that resting to the left of the sink.
Walk back over to the small grey trash can.
Place the green apple into the trash can to the right of the apple that is already in there.
